column1: Baby Barnaby's////The bf and I split the green eggs dish and the chicken fried steak. The chicken fried steak was chewy and not that appealing. I wouldn't recommend it at all even though the hostess did. Can't imagine why it's she would say it's one of their most ordered items. However
column2: the green eggs were delicious! Creamy
column3: delicious goodness scrambled with spinach and artichokes. The sausage was also good
column4: but I really enjoyed the seasoned potatoes. The potatoes reminded me of jack in the box curly fries
